1. *Lopov* je opljačkao dućan. (The thief robbed the store.)
2. Policija je uhvatila *lopova*. (The police caught the thief.)
3. On je bio poznat kao *lopov*. (He was known as a thief.)
4. *Lopovluk* je zabranjen. (Theft is forbidden.)
5. *Lopovlučki* činovi su kažnjivi. (Theft offences are punishable.)
6. On se počinio *lopovluka*. (He committed theft.)
7. Kako je moguće da je uspio u *lopovluku*? (How was he able to succeed in theft?)